Runs a command as a particular user. The special user '~console' can be used to run it as a console user. Using '~op' is deprecated, and will be removed after the next release, use sudo() instead. Commands cannot be run as an offline player. If the first argument is an array of usernames, the command will be run in the context of each user in the array.
